Integration Orchestration (Generally Available)

Review the status of the integration callouts by using Integration Orchestration. Additionally, add the Integration Execution Status lightning web component to your record page to manage the integration callouts.

Streamline Integration Callouts with Integration Orchestration
Use Integration Orchestration, which is now generally available, to dynamically create integration callout plans, and enable users to review the status of integrations with different external endpoints. Users can easily track the progress of all integration callouts, resulting in better process visibility and efficiency.

Visualize Integration Callouts and Manage Them Easily
Integration Orchestration now has a prebuilt Lightning Web Component. Add this component to your record page to give users a consolidated view of all the integration callouts. Users can easily manage manual and automatically triggered integrationsâ€“all at one place.
